    m 1eua "..."
    m 1tua "'Consider the practical effects of the objects of your conception. Then, your conception of those effects is the whole of your conception of the object.'"
    m 1hub "Ahaha! I know that sounds super formal, right?"
    m 3eub "But really, I think it just means that an idea's true meaning is all about its practical results."
    m 1eua "Like, think about when you're writing a speech for a class, or sharing a poem with everyone."
